---
---
<section id="servicios" class="py-40 relative z-10 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    
    <div class="mb-28 fade-up">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="h-px bg-white/20 w-16"></div>
        <div class="saas-badge border-none text-white/50 tracking-[0.2em] text-[0.7rem] px-0">Ingeniería de Valor</div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
        Multiplicamos su eficiencia <br/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white/60 to-white/20">a través del código.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Corporate Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10 auto-rows-[320px]">
      
      <!-- Card 1 (Span 2) -->
      <article class="bento-card md:col-span-2 p-12 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between group fade-up relative overflow-hidden" style="transition-delay: 0s">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-5 tracking-tight group-hover:text-[var(--saas-brand)] transition-colors duration-300">Arquitectura Digital Escalable</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-white/60 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-light">
            Construimos plataformas corporativas diseñadas para manejar millones de peticiones. Mitigamos el riesgo tecnológico de su empresa mediante bases de código sólidas, seguras y preparadas para el futuro.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 2 (Span 1) -->
      <article class="bento-card md:col-span-1 p-10 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-between group fade-up bg-[#8B1A2B]/10 border-[#8B1A2B]/30 hover:border-[#8B1A2B]/60 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(139,26,43,0.1)] hover:shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(139,26,43,0.2)]" style="transition-delay: 0.15s">
        <div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 border border-[#8B1A2B]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-10 bg-[#8B1A2B]/20 backdrop-blur-xl text-[#8B1A2B] rounded-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><path d="M3 6h18M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-5 tracking-tight group-hover:text-[#8B1A2B] transition-colors duration-300">Comercio B2B/B2C</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light">Sistemas transaccionales de alto volumen enfocados 100% en maximizar la tasa de conversión y el valor de vida del cliente.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 3 (Span 1) -->
      <article class="bento-card md:col-span-1 p-10 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-between group fade-up" style="transition-delay: 0.3s">
        <div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-5 tracking-tight group-hover:text-[var(--saas-brand)] transition-colors duration-300">Consultoría en IA</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-light">Reducción masiva de costos operativos mediante la integración estratégica de modelos de inteligencia artificial en flujos internos.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 4 (Span 2) -->
      <article class="bento-card md:col-span-2 p-12 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between group fade-up relative overflow-hidden" style="transition-delay: 0.45s">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 3v18M15 3v18M3 9h18M3 15h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-5 tracking-tight group-hover:text-[var(--saas-brand)] transition-colors duration-300">Sistemas ERP & Automatización</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-white/60 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-light">
            Destruimos la burocracia corporativa centralizando datos. Desarrollamos software de gestión a medida que automatiza procesos manuales, generando un ROI inmediato en ahorro de horas-hombre.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
